{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":779851,"duration_api_ms":833820,"num_turns":52,"result":"## 开发完成！\n\nPhase 2 和 Phase 3 的核心功能已完成。以下是本次开发的内容：\n\n### Phase 2：客户端功能 ✅\n- 客户注册流程（带店铺信息）\n- 客户仪表盘页面\n- 新建产品页面（表单 + 图片上传）\n- 产品列表页面\n- 产品详情页面\n- 点数余额展示 + 消耗确认\n- 成品图查看 + 下载功能\n\n### Phase 3：管理端功能 ✅\n- **管理后台布局** - 带导航的深色主题\n- **管理员仪表盘** - 平台统计、待处理任务、最近产品/交易\n- **客户管理** - 列表、详情、充值功能\n- **产品管理** - 全局视角、状态筛选\n- **图片审核** - 通过/淘汰/重新生成、批量操作\n- **交付确认** - 审核通过后交付给客户\n- **点数管理** - 系统总览、交易记录\n- **风格模板** - 模板展示\n\n### API 路由\n- `POST /api/admin/credits/recharge` - 充值点数\n- `POST /api/admin/products/[id]/deliver` - 交付产品\n- `PATCH /api/admin/images/[id]/review` - 审核图片\n\n### 路由结构\n```\n/admin          → 管理员仪表盘\n/admin/customers     → 客户列表\n/admin/customers/[id]  → 客户详情+充值\n/admin/products      → 产品列表\n/admin/products/[id]/review → 图片审核\n/admin/credits       → 点数管理\n/admin/styles        → 风格模板\n```\n\n项目已成功构建！如需测试可以运行 `npm run dev`。","session_id":"0fe3e04a-e649-4c3b-ad04-3a2fa78bad13","total_cost_usd":2.2346749499999996,"usage":{"input_tokens":25057,"cache_creation_input_tokens":124376,"cache_read_input_tokens":3884677,"output_tokens":31232,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0}},"modelUsage":{"MiniMax-M2.5":{"inputTokens":26719,"outputTokens":33835,"cacheReadInputTokens":3885889,"cacheCreationInputTokens":128327,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.2346749499999996,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"e0c038d3-03c0-4f63-853d-343da0885f62"}
